  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released Deployed\u00a0on 9/15/16 11:20 CT</p><p>This is a minor release with\u00a0a few bug fixes.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.6-SummaryReport\">Summary Report</h3><p>Tax group sum totals were\u00a0not\u00a0always summed correctly. This issue has been resolved.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.6-MiscellaneousAppSettingsAdditions\">Miscellaneous App Settings Additions</h3><p>We added a few new app settings to the &quot;Miscellaneous&quot; page to provide additional configuration controls.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Show All Locations on the Leaderboard:\u00a0</strong>When enabled, this setting will allow store managers to see all locations on the location leaderboard report.</p></li><li><p><strong>Allow viewing tickets from any location:</strong> When enabled,\u00a0this adds view-only access for\u00a0tickets at all locations, even where a user does not have roles assigned.</p></li></ul>",
